          Varansi Temple </h2>
        <p>
            <img alt="" class="style1" src="../../TourismHUB/Packages/Images/varansi.jpg" /></p>
        <p>
            India is quite famous as a place with a rich cultural heritage and history. Thanks to the various cities and towns that the country is home to. Talking about culture and heritage the first city that comes to mind when one comes to think of it is Varanasi Varanasi is one of those places that take pride in being the oldest yet the most diverse places in India. If somebody wants to taste the real India then Varanasi is a place that is not to be missed. There are many ghats, foods, Benarasi sarees that Varanasi is famous for. But the thing that attracts tourists from around the world is the temples in Varanasi has this holy, divine aura to itself that makes it a place that you will not want to miss ever!</p>
        <p>
